snippet.title: Gedaria | Raking leaves - game mechanic
snippet.description:
I’m happy that I can finally reveal one of the most important mechanics in our new czech indie game 😍 In this videos Vladimir has to rake the leaves to form a pile and to get higher 👆

Do you like our game? You can find more interesting videos on our Instagram profile 
@gedaria_official. Don‘t forget to follow us so that you don’t miss any other post.

IG : https://www.instagram.com/gedaria_official/
